# SecureAI local secrets. Copy to .dev.vars (gitignored) for `wrangler dev`.
# Non-secret tunables live in wrangler.jsonc `vars`, not here.
# Set real secrets in deploys with `wrangler secret put <NAME>`.

# Stripe (billing). Both secrets are REQUIRED for the /api/checkout,
# /api/portal, and /api/webhook routes; without them those routes return 503.
# Set them in production with `wrangler secret put STRIPE_SECRET_KEY` etc.
#   STRIPE_SECRET_KEY      — your Stripe secret API key (test or live mode).
#   STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET  — the signing secret of the /api/webhook endpoint,
#                            shown when you create the endpoint in the dashboard.
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...
# STRIPE_PRICE_PRO is a non-secret var (lives in wrangler.jsonc); override it
# here only to point local dev at a different Price. It is the $12/mo recurring
# Price id created in the Stripe dashboard.
# STRIPE_PRICE_PRO=price_...

# Threat-intel feed credentials, if a feed requires one (Spamhaus DROP does not).
# Workers AI needs no key — it uses the account `AI` binding.
